title: Ebro In The Morning - Happy Birthday Nas + White-Ish Wednesday
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 9/14/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio talking about Nas, playing White-Ish Wednesday, and did the Jets play themselves?

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
